title: Remember Favors? Vote MAGA Or Die! 2.3.20
itunes:title: Remember Favors? Vote MAGA Or Die! 2.3.20
description:
In episode 561, Jack and Miles are joined by comedian Steven Wilber to discuss the new 'Papadia' from Papa John's, Trump's Iowa rally, the gig-economy, Taylor Swift getting political in her music, Elon Musk's new EDM track, and more!

FOOTNOTES:

  1. Papa John’s debuts Shaquille O’Neal-approved flatbread sandwich, ‘Papadia’
  2. In Iowa, Trump threatens his fans that their farms will “go to hell” if he isn’t re-elected.
  3. “You’re going to make so much money” — This is the language of a mob boss, not a president
  4. TRUMP: "They want to kill our cows. That means you're next."
  5. The Help
  6. Taylor Swift’s New Song ‘Only the Young’ Encourages Fans to Get Political
  7. Elon Musk just dropped an EDM track on SoundCloud
  8. Don't Doubt ur Vibe - Emo G Records
  9. WATCH: KAYTRANADA - The Worst In Me (Audio) ft. Tinashe
